# Ghostty deploy

Whenever you change anything under `roles/ghostty/`, finish by running from the repo root:

```bash
ansible-playbook main.yml --tags ghostty
```

Do this in the same session as the code change unless the user explicitly asks to skip deploy. Do not only suggest the command—run it.
